	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=35651><span id=Guru>Keyeluke</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>680 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Quick answers:<br><br>You can group with any player character - no restrictions.&nbsp;&nbsp;You haven't left the Iksar newbie zone yet, so you're unlikely to see non-Iksar, except for travelers.<br><br>You should keep your hand-to-hand, 1 hand blunt, and 2 hand blunt up.  At higher levels, weapons clearly outperform your fists.  You don't have to worry about fresh weapons at different levels - they're not level dependent.  Read the boards and you'll learn a lot on this subject.  You have a cap on your skills, based on your level:  Level*5+5 for most skills.<br><br>Be cautious of preconceptions about the class, or any class for that matter.  Monks are better at hand-to-hand than any other class, but that doesn't mean that our hand-to-hand is better than the weapons available to us.</p>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Member of Tenacity - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></td></tr>
